insert into latest_data_to_be_processed_pat(exam_code) (select distinct exam_code from ((select exam_code from periodic_exam_mst where updated_on>(select max(end_date_time) from pat_processing_info) or created_on>(select max(end_date_time) from pat_processing_info)) union (select pem.exam_code from periodic_exam_qst_mst peqm join periodic_exam_mst pem on peqm.exam_id=pem.exam_id where peqm.updated_on>(select max(end_date_time) from pat_processing_info) or peqm.created_on>(select max(end_date_time) from pat_processing_info)) union (SELECT distinct exam_code from periodic_exam_result_staging_2) union (select exam_codes_list from pat_processing_info where status!='SUCCESS' and start_date_time >= (select max(start_date_time) from pat_processing_info where status='SUCCESS' )))as a);
